<block wx:if="{{$taroCompReady}}">
    <view class="getintegral-container">
        <view class="getintegral-header"><text class="getintegral-notice">公告：</text>如果有任何疑问，请拨打客服电话：<text class="getintegral-tel" bindtap="anonymousFunc0">{{SERVERPHONE}}</text><text class="getintegral-tel-copy" bindtap="anonymousFunc1">呼叫</text>。鱼泡网投入大量的人力物力开发平台、审核信息，免费服务千万工友。因此请大家帮忙多邀请工友注册，感谢您对鱼泡网的支持！</view>
        <view class="getintegral-body">
            <view class="getintegral-title">如何获取积分</view>
            <view class="getintegral-item">
                <view class="getintegral-item-title">邀请工友获取积分</view>
                <view class="getintegral-item-content">每成功邀请一位工友注册，最高可获得2-18积分。（推荐）</view>
                <view class="getintegral-item-btn" bindtap="anonymousFunc2">去邀请</view>
            </view>
            <block wx:if="{{!ios}}">
                <view class="getintegral-item">
                    <view class="getintegral-item-title">充值获取积分</view>
                    <view class="getintegral-item-content">充值付钱购买积分。（我们不鼓励付钱购买，我们希望大家多帮忙宣传）</view>
                    <view class="getintegral-item-btn" bindtap="anonymousFunc3">去充值</view>
                </view>
            </block>
        </view>
    </view>
</block>